# Clean install (from repo root)

**PowerShell (Windows):**
```powershell
cd apps/driver; if (Test-Path node_modules) { Remove-Item -Recurse -Force node_modules }; npm install
cd apps/passenger; if (Test-Path node_modules) { Remove-Item -Recurse -Force node_modules }; npm install
```

**Bash (Git Bash / WSL):**
```bash
cd apps/driver && rm -rf node_modules && npm install
cd apps/passenger && rm -rf node_modules && npm install
```

# Validate

**PowerShell:**
```powershell
cd apps/driver; npx expo-doctor@latest; npx tsc --noEmit
cd apps/passenger; npx expo-doctor@latest
```

**Bash:**
```bash
cd apps/driver && npx expo-doctor@latest && npx tsc --noEmit
cd apps/passenger && npx expo-doctor@latest
```

# EAS build (Android APK for testing)

**PowerShell:** (use `npx eas-cli` if `eas` is not in PATH)
```powershell
cd apps/driver; npx eas-cli build --platform android --profile preview --non-interactive
cd apps/passenger; npx eas-cli build --platform android --profile preview --non-interactive
```

**Bash:**
```bash
cd apps/driver && eas build --platform android --profile preview --non-interactive
cd apps/passenger && eas build --platform android --profile preview --non-interactive
```

